Jon Hamkins

   Supervisor, Information Processing Group
   Communications Systems and Research Section
   Ph.D., Electrical and Computer Engineering, University of Illinois at
   Urbana-Champaign, 1996
     __________________________________________________________________

   Research Interests

   Source and channel coding theory, information theory, optical
   communications, modulation, synchronization, and computational
   complexity theory.
     __________________________________________________________________

   Current Projects
     * Coding and Modulation for Optical Communications (PI)
     * Symbol Detection and Synchronization Algorithms for
       Laboratory-Collected Optical Photodetector Data (PI)
     * Coupled Receiver Decoder (Co-I)
